@startuml TurboSearch Workflow

title TurboSearch Search & Index Workflow

actor User
participant GUI
participant Searcher
participant ContentSearcher
participant FileIndex
participant "OS/FileSystem"

== Indexing Process ==

User -> GUI: 选择文件夹路径
GUI -> FileIndex: walk_directory_limited()
FileIndex -> "OS/FileSystem": 遍历目录
"OS/FileSystem" -> FileIndex: 返回文件列表
FileIndex -> FileIndex: 创建FileEntry列表
FileIndex -> GUI: 返回索引结果

== Search Process (Filename) ==

User -> GUI: 输入搜索关键词
GUI -> Searcher: search(query, index)
alt 模糊搜索
    Searcher -> Searcher: fuzzy_search()
    Searcher -> Searcher: SkimMatcherV2匹配
else 正则搜索
    Searcher -> Searcher: regex_search()
    Searcher -> Searcher: get_cached_regex()\n(使用DashMap缓存)
else Glob搜索
    Searcher -> Searcher: glob_search()
end
Searcher -> GUI: 返回匹配的FileEntry列表
GUI -> User: 显示搜索结果

== Search Process (Content) ==

User -> GUI: 选择内容搜索模式
GUI -> ContentSearcher: search(query, path)
ContentSearcher -> "OS/FileSystem": 打开文件
loop 逐行读取
    ContentSearcher -> ContentSearcher: 匹配行
end
ContentSearcher -> GUI: 返回ContentMatch列表
GUI -> User: 显示匹配内容和行号

== Preview Process ==

User -> GUI: 选择文件预览
GUI -> "OS/FileSystem": read_file_content()
alt 文本文件
    "OS/FileSystem" --> GUI: 返回文本内容
else 二进制文件
    "OS/FileSystem" --> GUI: 返回文件信息
end
GUI -> GUI: highlighted_content = 语法高亮
GUI -> User: 显示预览

== Memory Optimizations ==

note right of Searcher
  内存优化:
  1. DashMap缓存Regex
  2. 预计算to_lowercase
  3. SizeFilter使用u64哨兵值
end note

note right of GUI
  内存优化:
  1. 移除重复HashSet
  2. 限制结果显示数量
  3. 流式处理搜索结果
end note

@enduml
